high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the stove, hang a left and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife that is in the sink.
Turn to the left to the microwave.
Open the microwave, use the knife to cut the apple, close the microwave.
Lower the knife towards the counter.
Open the microwave, put the knife inside, close the door.
Raise up towards the microwave.
Open the microwave and remove a slice of apple, close the door.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge on the left.
Open the freezer, put the apple inside, close the door, then remove the cold apple from the freezer.
Turn to the left, go forward to the microwave.
Put the cold apple inside the microwave and close the door.

high_descs: Turn around and walk in the direction of the stove and hang a right to the sink.
Pick up the knife that is in the sink.
Turn to your left to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, slice the apple that is on the blue plate inside, close the door.
Open the microwave door.
Place the knife at the front of the blue plate in the microwave.
Close the microwave door.
Open the microwave door and pick up a wedge of the apple, close the door.
Turn to your right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the apple in the top bin on the left side of the fridge, close the door; after cooling open the door and pick up the apple wedge, close the door.
Turn to your left and walk to the microwave.
Open the door and place the apple wedge on the blue plate, close the door.
